of Tsushima]]," there is a similar shrine. It is the Scarlet Rock Shrine. The real shrine is dedicated to two deities, [[Hikohohodemi no Mikoto]] and [[Toyotama-hime|Toyotamabime]]. The game's shrine is dedicated to [[Tsukuyomi-no-Mikoto|Tsukuyomi]].<ref name="vgc-2021a" />
==See also== *[[Kaijin Shrine]] *[[Mihashira Torii]]
